text: Helpful and friendly staff. Prices here are also good. Pharmacist is very efficient and knowledgeable. They are smaller than most pharmacies but i think they have everything you need without being fancy.

Was greeted warmly by a male staff when I first stepped into the pharmacy. After I pointed my freshly wounded knee to him, he quickly offered me a seat and together with a kind lady pharmacist immediately sprang into action to help me with picking up medical supplies and dressings for my wounded knee. They even assisted with dressing up the wound and gave calm assurances. I am grateful for their kind and compassionate gestures. Without doubt the friendly and kind staff made my day despite the pain I suffered from the wound.
Staffs are knowledgeable, helpful and friendly. Well attended by them. Would recommend to go here.
Loves the service by the staff especially one of the workers afiq azizi, really helpful!
good services provided by pharmacists, would highly recommend people come here
